HEADWORD: Juggling
<hw>Jug"gling</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Cheating;
tricky.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>Jug"gling*ly</wf>,
<pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
